               <head>Sarmad, ruba'iyat</head>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Rubāʿīyāt-i Sarmad by Muḥammad Saʿīd Kāshānī "Sarmad"</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85109764 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh85129656 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2006003812 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh89005046 http://lccn.loc.gov/sh2013000323" n="1" xml:id="Uk_IO_Islamic_4059-item1">
